handle_4G

Description:
This module is used to handle 4G connectivity for the device.

Functions:
- check_sim_status()
- fetch_sim_info()
- check_signal_strength()
- connect_network()
- reconnect_network()
- send_data_mqtt()

Purpose:
This handler ensures that the device stays connected to the internet using 4G LTE module.
It also checks SIM status, signal strength, and reconnects automatically if network fails.

